text: The curry is very good and the portion is big enough for a male adult. This is a balanced plate of curry rice with meat, veggie, egg, and rice. They use the more expensive Japanese rice that adds more flavor to the dish however the rice today was a little too moist. Highly recommend this if you crave a good Singapore style curry with a good piece of meat.
The curry rice with double meat (pork and chicken) is yummy and affordable.
Crispy chicken cutlet & spicy curry - an excellent combo!
